{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/nintendo-2ds-saudara-3ds-yang-kadang-dipandang-sebelah-mata/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Nintendo 2DS: Saudara 3DS Yang (Kadang) Dipandang Sebelah Mata","content":"\n<p>Nintendo 2DS. Apa kamu pernah mendengar nama itu? Konsol game ini muncul beberapa lama setelah Nintendo 3DS hadir dan menguasai pasar konsol game handheld. Mengapa Nintendo merilis 2DS justru setelah Nintendo 3DS sukses di pasaran? Dan apa perbedanya dengan Nintendo 3DS?</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53397\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-2ds-saudara-3ds-yang-kadang-dipandang-sebelah-mata/attachment/01-rewards-2ds/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-rewards-2ds.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-rewards-2ds\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-rewards-2ds.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-rewards-2ds.jpg\" alt=\"Nintendo 3DS. Sumber: Wikimedia\" class=\"wp-image-53397\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-rewards-2ds.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Nintendo 3DS. Sumber: Wikimedia</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai latar belakang, Nintendo 3DS merupakan konsol\nhandheld Nintendo yang menjadi penerus dari keluarga Nintendo DS. 3DS memiliki\nfitur yang mirip dengan Nintendo DS standar, seperti dua layar dengan fitur\ntouch screen di layar bawah dengan desain bodi clamshell. Perbedaannya,\nNintendo 3DS memiliki fitur 3D dalam setiap gamenya! Gamer bisa melihat efek 3D\ntanpa menggunakan kacamata, serta adanya dua kamera memungkinkan gamer\nmengambil foto dalam format 3D.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53398\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-2ds-saudara-3ds-yang-kadang-dipandang-sebelah-mata/attachment/02-rewards-2ds/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-rewards-2ds.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-rewards-2ds\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-rewards-2ds.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-rewards-2ds.jpg\" alt=\"Nintendo 2DS. Sumber: Wikimedia\" class=\"wp-image-53398\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-rewards-2ds.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Nintendo 2DS. Sumber: Wikimedia</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Nintendo 2DS rilis pada tahun 2013, dua tahun setelah Nintendo 3DS. 2DS memiliki spesifikasi hardware dan software yang serupa. Gamer bisa memainkan berbagai game Nintendo 3DS dan DS biasa dalam Nintendo 2DS. Perbedaan signifikan dari 2DS adalah desain bodi yang solid dan serupa dengan joystick Nintendo Wii U yang berlayar. Selain itu, fitur 3D dalam game tidak bisa diakses.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Saat Nintendo 2DS dirilis, beberapa gamer mengeluhkan kualitas dari konsol tersebut yang dianggap downgrade dari Nintendo 3DS. Desain yang biasa serta kualitas audio yang menurun jadi alasan utama yang membuat orang enggan mencoba 2DS. Namun, kelebihan dari 2DS mampu menutupi kelemahan tersebut. Nggak percaya? </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"45759\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/know-your-judges-1-fajar-ghosty/attachment/05-fajar-ghosty/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-fajar-ghosty.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-fajar-ghosty\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-fajar-ghosty-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-fajar-ghosty.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-fajar-ghosty.jpg\" alt=\"Fajar Ghosty dikelilingi memorabilia Pokemon. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-45759\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-fajar-ghosty.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-fajar-ghosty-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Fajar Ghosty dikelilingi memorabilia Pokemon. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk menjelaskan berbagai kelebihan 2DS, CIAYO Blog mengundang Fajar Ghosty, komikus <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"GHOSTY’s Comic (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GHOSTY.COMIC/\" target=\"_blank\">GHOSTY’s Comic</a> yang juga seorang fans berat Nintendo. Apa sih pendapat Fajar soal Nintendo 2DS?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>“Buat kamu yang risih dengan bentuk 3DS biasa yang berengsel\ndan takut patah, kamu tidak perlu mengkhawatirkan itu di 2DS, karena tidak ada\nengsel sama sekali,” jawab Fajar. “Mesinnya pun terasa kokoh sehingga kamu ga\nperlu takut bakal cepat rusak. Selain itu, 2DS ini bisa memainkan seluruh game\n3DS (selain game khusus untuk New 3DS), jadi kamu tetap bisa memainkan\ngame-game 3DS yang kamu mau di 2DS.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lalu, untuk siapa sih 2DS ini dibuat? Kenapa harus dibedakan antara 2DS dan 3DS kalau sebenarnya antara keduanya nggak jauh berbeda?</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53399\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-2ds-saudara-3ds-yang-kadang-dipandang-sebelah-mata/attachment/03-rewards-2ds/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-rewards-2ds.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-rewards-2ds\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-rewards-2ds.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-rewards-2ds.jpg\" alt=\"Anak-anak bermain Nintendo 2DS. Sumber: Niche Gamer\" class=\"wp-image-53399\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-rewards-2ds.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Anak-anak bermain Nintendo 2DS. Sumber: Niche Gamer</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>“Tentunya untuk gamer yang ingin merasakan main game\nberkualitas tinggi di mana saja, karena 2DS bisa dibawa ke mana saja,” lanjut\nFajar. “Bagi yang ingin merasakan nostalgia main Super Mario Bros., Pokemon,\ndan The Legend of Zelda, game-game barunya bisa dimainkan di 2DS. 2DS pun aman\ndipakai untuk anak-anak, jadi buat para papah muda yang ingin ngenalin anaknya\nmain game bisa dikenalin lewat 2DS.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Terakhir, game apa aja yang bisa dan wajib dimainin di 2DS? Fajar Ghosty punya daftar game yang harus kamu mainin kalau punya Nintendo 2DS.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Game Nintendo 2DS Yang Wajib Kamu Mainin</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53400\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-2ds-saudara-3ds-yang-kadang-dipandang-sebelah-mata/attachment/04-rewards-2ds/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-rewards-2ds.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-rewards-2ds\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-rewards-2ds.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-rewards-2ds.jpg\" alt=\"Super Mario 3D Land. Sumber: Stmed\" class=\"wp-image-53400\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-rewards-2ds.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Super Mario 3D Land. Sumber: Stmed</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Super\nMario 3D Land:</strong> Ingin merasakan main Super Mario jadul tapi versi 3D?\nMainkan game ini!</li><li><strong>Pokemon\nSun and Moon:</strong> Pokemon sekarang sudah sangat maju, lebih dari 800 Pokemon\ndan sudah 3D. Semua bisa kamu rasakan di Pokemon Sun and Moon.</li><li><strong>Kirby\nPlanet Robobot:</strong> Buat kamu yang ingin game yang tidak terlalu challenging\ntapi tetap seru, Kirby Planet Robobot ini cocok untuk kamu.</li><li><strong>Super\nSmash Bros. for 3DS:</strong> Ingin lihat berbagai karakter Nintendo gebuk-gebukan\nbareng Sonic, Megaman, dan Pac-Man? Semua ada di Smash Bros.</li><li><strong>Animal\nCrossing New Leaf:</strong> Ini cocok banget buat kamu yang cuma ingin main santai\ntanpa ada beban. Mirip The Sims tapi kamu ga perlu khawatir perlu makan, tidur,\ndan sebagainya.</li><li><strong>Monster\nHunter 4 Ultimate:</strong> Buat kamu yang ingin game action yang sangat challenging\ndan penuh monster-monster raksasa, ini cocok untuk kamu!</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53401\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nintendo-2ds-saudara-3ds-yang-kadang-dipandang-sebelah-mata/attachment/05-rewards-2ds/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-rewards-2ds.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-rewards-2ds\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-rewards-2ds.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-rewards-2ds.jpg\" alt=\"Sebagian game Nintendo 3DS dan 2DS dibuat di Jepang. Sumber: GHOSTY’s Comic\" class=\"wp-image-53401\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-rewards-2ds.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-rewards-2ds-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sebagian game Nintendo 3DS dan 2DS dibuat di Jepang. Sumber: GHOSTY’s Comic</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Nah, itu dia cerita tentang Nintendo 2DS, berbagai kelebihannya, serta game apa saja yang wajib dimainin. Terima kasih buat Fajar Ghosty untuk penjelasannya! Jika kamu penasaran seberapa asyiknya main 2DS tapi kamu nggak punya uang untuk beli atau teman untuk dipinjamin, jangan kuatir! Kamu berkesempatan mendapatkan Nintendo 2DS dengan bonus game Yo-Kai Watch dengan mengikuti CIAYO Comics REWARDS! </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53258\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-kembali-dengan-hadiah-yang-lebih-menarik/attachment/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg\" alt=\"01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus\" class=\"wp-image-53258\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-ciayo-comics-rewards-plus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\